WEBVTT

00:01.502 --> 00:02.673
PREVIOUSLY ON "REVENGE"...
 NO!

00:02.673 --> 00:04.585
Jack: LET HER GO!

00:04.585 --> 00:06.677
YOU AND EMILY
DESERVE A LIFE TOGETHER.

00:06.677 --> 00:08.219
I NEED TO MOURN MY SON.

00:08.219 --> 00:09.840
I'M NOT SURE IT'LL BE
THAT EASY

00:09.840 --> 00:11.432
TO EXPLAIN ALL OF THIS
TO BEN.

00:11.432 --> 00:13.054
IT'LL BE EASIER
THAN YOU THINK.

00:13.054 --> 00:14.185
ALL THIS TIME,
I THOUGHT THE REASON

00:14.185 --> 00:15.516
YOU WERE ALWAYS ACTING
SO WEIRD AROUND ME

00:15.516 --> 00:16.517
WAS BECAUSE OF ME.

00:16.517 --> 00:17.688
NOT TRUE.

00:17.688 --> 00:18.849
SO WHAT DO YOU SAY,
BEGINNING TOMORROW,

00:18.849 --> 00:19.850
WE START OVER?

00:19.850 --> 00:21.352
I'D LIKE THAT VERY MUCH.
[ CHUCKLES ]

00:21.352 --> 00:24.235
THERE'S A WOMAN WHO NEEDS
TO PAY FOR CROSSING ME.

00:24.235 --> 00:25.736
ALL I NEED'S A NAME
AND A NUMBER.

00:25.736 --> 00:26.817
I GET QUICK RESULTS.

00:26.817 --> 00:28.319
GIVE YOUR MAMA A HUG.

00:28.319 --> 00:31.702
YOU BREATHE A WORD ABOUT
THE DOSING AND SHE CUTS YOU OFF?

00:31.702 --> 00:32.743
Louise:
SOUNDS ABOUT RIGHT.

00:32.743 --> 00:33.994
MY LEGAL TEAM
FOUND A LOOPHOLE.

00:33.994 --> 00:35.746
YOU ONLY REMAIN
IN CHARGE OF YOUR DAUGHTER...

00:35.746 --> 00:36.997
UNTIL SHE FINDS
A HUSBAND.

00:36.997 --> 00:38.209
GUESS
WHO JUST GOT MARRIED.

00:38.209 --> 00:40.000
YOU WILL
GIVE ME CONTROL BACK,

00:40.000 --> 00:41.832
OR THE REAL TRUTH
WILL COME OUT.

00:41.832 --> 00:43.504
YOU KILLED YOUR FATHER.

00:46.006 --> 00:48.129
Emily:
NOLAN ROSS MARRIED.

00:48.129 --> 00:50.381
Nolan:
WELL, WHAT CAN I SAY?

00:50.381 --> 00:51.512
YOU MISS SOME THINGS

00:51.512 --> 00:53.174
WHEN YOU GET KIDNAPPED
BY A SOCIOPATH.

00:53.174 --> 00:54.675
YOU KNOW,
THERE ARE SOME PEOPLE

00:54.675 --> 00:56.767
WHO SAY THE EXACT SAME THING
HAPPENED TO YOU.

00:56.767 --> 00:58.439
HEY, LOUISE IS
NO MALCOLM BLACK --

00:58.439 --> 01:00.731
OR SHOULD I SAY
MALCOLM BLACKER

01:00.731 --> 01:03.394
AFTER HIS CONFAB
WITH THAT INCINERATOR.

01:03.394 --> 01:05.646
BESIDES,
YOU SECRETLY ADORE HER.

01:05.646 --> 01:07.568
WHY ELSE WOULD YOU
THROW OPEN YOUR HOME

01:07.568 --> 01:09.360
FOR YOUR BESTIE'S
WEDDING RECEPTION?

01:09.360 --> 01:10.861
UH,
 FAKE WEDDING RECEPTION.

01:10.861 --> 01:13.614
OKAY, THE MARRIAGE
MAY BE FAKE IN SPIRIT,

01:13.614 --> 01:15.286
BUT IT'S REAL
ON PAPER.

01:15.286 --> 01:16.907
NOLAN ROSS IS...

01:18.369 --> 01:19.830
...OFF THE MARKET.

01:19.830 --> 01:21.332
AND THE WORLD WEEPS.

01:21.332 --> 01:22.703
BUT NOT LOUISE.

01:22.703 --> 01:26.417
SHE'S FINALLY FREE OF THE
CLUTCHES OF PENELOPE DREADFUL,

01:26.417 --> 01:28.549
RIGHTFULLY OWNS
HER FAMILY FORTUNE.

01:28.549 --> 01:31.672
WHICH, GIVEN THE SIZE OF
THIS PARTY AND THE GUEST LIST,

01:31.672 --> 01:32.883
SHE'S ALREADY SPENT.

01:32.883 --> 01:34.135
SPEAKING OF...

01:34.135 --> 01:36.927
IN HER ZEAL,
MY LOVELY BETTER HALF

01:36.927 --> 01:40.681
INVITED EVERY MAJOR MEDIA OUTLET
TO COVER THE PARTY --

01:40.681 --> 01:43.274
INCLUDING MARGAUX,
WHO RSVP'd OUI.

01:43.274 --> 01:46.647
WAIT -- WASN'T THERE A
NEAR-DEATH STEAM-ROOM INCIDENT?

01:46.647 --> 01:48.068
AH, YES.
THE HAMPTONS.

01:48.068 --> 01:50.821
IF YOU DON'T PRETEND
TO FORGIVE EVERYONE YOU HATE,

01:50.821 --> 01:52.653
YOU NEVER
GET INVITED ANYWHERE.

01:52.653 --> 01:54.495
WHAT, DO YOU WANT ME
TO EXERCISE MY SPOUSAL VETO?

01:54.495 --> 01:55.736
NO.

01:55.736 --> 01:57.998
IT'S BEEN DAYS SINCE MARGAUX
LEARNED THE FULL TRUTH,

01:57.998 --> 01:59.830
AND SHE HASN'T SAID
OR DONE ANYTHING ABOUT IT.

01:59.830 --> 02:00.951
[ CELLPHONE CHIMES ]

02:00.951 --> 02:03.164
SO, WHAT'S NEXT
FOR EMILY THORNE,

02:03.164 --> 02:06.006
NOW THAT DANGER NO LONGER
LURKS AROUND EVERY CORNER?

02:06.006 --> 02:07.047
[ SIGHS ]

02:07.047 --> 02:09.049
STILL GOING
TO MY FATHER'S RESCUE.

02:09.049 --> 02:10.751
[ CHUCKLES ]
 SEE YOU LATER.

02:12.843 --> 02:14.885
Reporter:
A TRULY HEROIC STORY.

02:14.885 --> 02:17.558
THAT'S OFFICER BEN HUNTER,
ONE OF TWO SUPERCOPS

02:17.558 --> 02:19.680
WHO TOOK DOWN
CHIEF ALVAREZ'S KILLER

02:19.680 --> 02:21.392
AND RESCUED
THREE HOSTAGES.

02:21.392 --> 02:23.143
THANK YOU
FOR KEEPING US SAFE.

02:23.143 --> 02:25.816
I'M JUST DOING MY JOB.

02:25.816 --> 02:27.688
WHICH I SHOULD GET TO,
IT BEING OUR FIRST DAY BACK.

02:27.688 --> 02:28.819
SO THANK YOU.

02:28.819 --> 02:30.571
OH,
OFFICER PORTER!

02:30.571 --> 02:32.363
CARE TO SAY A FEW WORDS?

02:32.363 --> 02:33.364
[ SIGHS ]

02:33.364 --> 02:34.985
HEY, YOU STILL
DUCKING THE CAMERAS?

02:34.985 --> 02:36.537
NOT EVERYONE
NEEDS THE ATTENTION.

02:36.537 --> 02:39.540
HUNTER, PORTER, NEED TO SEE YOU
IN THE BULLPEN.

02:41.872 --> 02:44.375
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

02:49.340 --> 02:51.502
THIS DEPARTMENT
OWES YOU A DEBT OF GRATITUDE,

02:51.502 --> 02:52.843
WHICH IS WHY TOMORROW,

02:52.843 --> 02:55.676
THE MAYOR IS PRESENTING YOU
WITH MEDALS OF HONOR.

02:55.676 --> 02:57.258
I'M SORRY, CHIEF,
I CAN'T MAKE IT.

02:57.258 --> 02:58.889
I GOT A FRIEND'S
WEDDING RECEPTION.

02:58.889 --> 03:01.302
SO BE LATE, PORTER.
THE MAYOR DOESN'T RESCHEDULE.

03:01.302 --> 03:02.433
I WOULDN'T EXPECT HIM TO.

03:02.433 --> 03:03.934
YOU CAN ACCEPT
FOR BOTH OF US.

03:03.934 --> 03:06.227
GOT TO CLOCK IN.

03:07.768 --> 03:10.691
I NEED MAYOR LAKEN'S CONFIDENCE
IN THIS DEPARTMENT.

03:10.691 --> 03:13.113
MAKE SURE
YOUR PARTNER'S THERE TOMORROW.

03:13.113 --> 03:16.156
WILL DO, CHIEF.

03:16.156 --> 03:18.118
Margaux: I RECEIVED
YOUR INVITATION --

03:18.118 --> 03:21.081
A FUNDRAISER FOR
THE DANIEL GRAYSON FOUNDATION?

03:21.081 --> 03:24.705
HONORING DANIEL'S MEMORY
IS MOST IMPORTANT TO ME NOW.

03:24.705 --> 03:26.206
SO THIS MEANS
YOU PLAN TO COME CLEAN

03:26.206 --> 03:28.829
ABOUT THE TRUTH
REGARDING DANIEL'S DEATH?

03:28.829 --> 03:30.130
I CAN'T, MARGAUX.

03:30.130 --> 03:33.544
AS MUCH AS IT GOES AGAINST
MY EVERY INSTINCT,

03:33.544 --> 03:36.176
I MADE A PROMISE,
AND I HAVE TO KEEP IT.

03:36.176 --> 03:39.260
SO HELP ME UNDERSTAND
HOW A FOUNDATION

03:39.260 --> 03:43.474
IN THE NAME OF A MAN INFAMOUS
FOR ASSAULTING HIS EX-WIFE

03:43.474 --> 03:45.225
WILL HONOR HIS MEMORY?

03:45.225 --> 03:46.687
BY HELPING
DISADVANTAGED CHILDREN

03:46.687 --> 03:48.058
BECOME TOMORROW'S LEADERS.

03:48.058 --> 03:51.692
THE FOUNDATION WILL EVENTUALLY
TRANSFORM DANIEL'S NAME

03:51.692 --> 03:55.356
FROM ONE OF INFAMY...
TO ONE OF GOODNESS.

03:55.356 --> 03:57.618
I KNOW YOU,
VICTORIA.

03:57.618 --> 04:01.492
YOU ALSO BELIEVE THAT
JUSTICE SHOULD BE SERVED,

04:01.492 --> 04:03.203
SO WHILE I WILL RESPECT
YOUR FIDELITY

04:03.203 --> 04:07.498
TO A PROMISE YOU HAVE MADE,
MINE IS TO CLEAR DANIEL'S NAME.

04:07.498 --> 04:10.170
I TOLD YOU THAT
IF YOU GO TO WAR TO WITH EMILY,

04:10.170 --> 04:11.672
NO GOOD
CAN COME OF IT.

04:13.464 --> 04:15.546
TRUST ME --
PAIN AND CONFLICT

04:15.546 --> 04:18.469
ONLY BRINGS
MORE PAIN AND CONFLICT.

04:18.469 --> 04:21.642
SO MOVE FORWARD
FOR YOU AND YOUR CHILD.

04:21.642 --> 04:25.145
IT IS FOR THE TWO OF US
THAT I MUST DO THIS.

04:25.145 --> 04:27.558
I HOPE
YOU RECONSIDER.

04:29.019 --> 04:32.152
[ POP MUSIC PLAYS ]

04:32.152 --> 04:33.944
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

04:33.944 --> 04:35.155
[ SIGHS ] WELL...

04:35.155 --> 04:37.658
I WAS WONDERING
HOW LONG IT WOULD TAKE

04:37.658 --> 04:39.990
BEFORE MAMA BARKED
FOR HER LAPDOG.

04:39.990 --> 04:41.862
BABY SIS
GOT HITCHED TO A YANKEE.

04:41.862 --> 04:44.034
YOU THINK
I'M GONNA MISS THAT CLAMBAKE?

04:44.034 --> 04:46.457
[ CHUCKLES ]

04:46.457 --> 04:49.910
NOW, LOU, I HAD NO IDEA WHAT
MAMA WAS DOING TO YOUR PILLS.

04:49.910 --> 04:50.911
I SWEAR.

04:50.911 --> 04:52.833
I'M ONLY HERE
TO BROKER PEACE.

04:52.833 --> 04:55.876
WELL, PEACE REQUIRES
A COMPROMISE,

04:55.876 --> 04:59.340
WHICH IS SOMETHING OUR DEAR
MOTHER IS UTTERLY INCAPABLE OF.

04:59.340 --> 05:01.882
BE THAT AS IT MAY, SHE DOES HAVE
YOUR BEST INTERESTS AT HEART.

05:01.882 --> 05:03.474
DOES SHE, NOW?

05:03.474 --> 05:08.308
DO YOU HAVE ANY IDEA
THE LIES THAT SHE'S TOLD ME?

05:09.850 --> 05:11.101
THEY'RE NOT LIES.

05:11.101 --> 05:12.983
[ SIGHS ]
 THAT'S FOR YOU.

05:12.983 --> 05:15.235
THAT'S THE POLICE REPORT
FROM THE NIGHT DADDY DIED.

05:15.235 --> 05:18.198
HOW HAVE I NEVER
SEEN THIS BEFORE?

05:18.198 --> 05:19.990
MAMA HAD IT BURIED
BY JUDGE MILLER.

05:19.990 --> 05:21.281
OH.

05:21.281 --> 05:24.365
SO THAT'S WHY HE'S HER PLUS-ONE
TOMORROW NIGHT.

05:24.365 --> 05:25.866
IF YOU DON'T
RESTORE THE CONSERVATORSHIP,

05:25.866 --> 05:28.038
SHE INTENDS TO RELEASE
THE REPORT AT YOUR RECEPTION --

05:28.038 --> 05:29.329
POETIC JUSTICE,
SHE SAYS,

05:29.329 --> 05:31.412
CONSIDERING YOU GOT MARRIED
JUST TO THWART HER.

05:31.412 --> 05:33.163
OH, THE THREATS
AND COERCION.

05:33.163 --> 05:34.505
[ SIGHS ]

05:34.505 --> 05:36.717
I SHOULD'VE KNOWN --
YOU ALWAYS TAKE MAMA'S SIDE.

05:36.717 --> 05:38.008
THERE'S NO SIDES HERE,
LOU.

05:38.008 --> 05:40.511
T-THERE'S JUST FACTS.
YOU...

05:40.511 --> 05:42.553
HE WAS MY FATHER,
TOO.

05:42.553 --> 05:46.346
BUT I COULDN'T HAVE
KILLED HIM, LYMAN.

05:46.346 --> 05:49.430
I KNOW
HOW MUCH YOU LOVED HIM,

05:49.430 --> 05:51.682
BUT YOU'RE IMPULSIVE,
QUICK TO ANGER.

05:51.682 --> 05:53.394
YOU KNOW
YOU'RE CAPABLE OF IT.

05:53.394 --> 05:54.475
JUST SIGN
THE ANNULMENT.

05:54.475 --> 05:57.357
SO YOUR MONEY TAP
STAYS ON

05:57.357 --> 05:59.650
AND YOU CAN CONTINUE
TO FINANCE YOUR CAMPAIGN?

05:59.650 --> 06:01.361
I MEAN,
THAT'S ALL YOU CARE ABOUT.

06:01.361 --> 06:02.613
NO,
I CARE ABOUT YOU.

06:02.613 --> 06:05.195
WHAT'S YOUR LIFE GONNA LOOK LIKE
IF THIS COMES OUT?

06:05.195 --> 06:06.697
DO YOU REALLY THINK
YOUR FAKE HUSBAND'S

06:06.697 --> 06:08.989
GONNA STAND BY YOU?

06:08.989 --> 06:11.161
READ THE REPORT, LOU. SAVE US
ALL A LOT OF EMBARRASSMENT.

06:19.169 --> 06:21.802
YOUR LEG'S HEALING.

06:21.802 --> 06:25.716
THE LIMP IS BETTER, WHICH MEANS
YOU CAN SAVE ME A DANCE.

06:25.716 --> 06:27.848
ONE STEP AT A TIME,
YOU KNOW?

06:27.848 --> 06:30.771
WHICH TIE SHOULD I WEAR
TO THE FIRST PARTY

06:30.771 --> 06:33.063
THAT I HAVE BEEN TO
IN 20 YEARS?

06:33.063 --> 06:35.395
WELL, THE BLUE ONE
IS THE ONLY ONE

06:35.395 --> 06:38.108
THAT MATCHES THAT SUIT --
AND YOUR EYES.

06:38.108 --> 06:42.402
NEVER DREAMED THAT I'D
BE STANDING HERE AGAIN WITH YOU.

06:42.402 --> 06:45.696
I MISSED OUT
ON SO MUCH OF YOUR LIFE.

06:45.696 --> 06:48.789
WELL, WE FINALLY HAVE THE TIME
TO MAKE UP FOR IT.

06:48.789 --> 06:51.872
AND I KNOW
WHERE I WANT TO START...

06:51.872 --> 06:56.296
YOUR BIRTHDAY -- THE ONE
THAT I MISSED A FEW DAYS AGO

06:56.296 --> 06:58.799
AND SADLY HAVE
FOR THE LAST 20 YEARS.

06:58.799 --> 07:01.672
WHAT'S THIS?

07:01.672 --> 07:04.805
"AMANDA CLARKE."

07:08.809 --> 07:13.183
I HAVEN'T CELEBRATED
MY REAL BIRTHDAY IN...

07:13.183 --> 07:14.815
WELL, FOREVER.

07:14.815 --> 07:16.186
[ CHUCKLES ]

07:16.186 --> 07:18.609
WELL, MAYBE IT'S TIME
TO CHANGE THAT --

07:18.609 --> 07:20.481
YOU KNOW,
TO BE AMANDA AGAIN,

07:20.481 --> 07:23.774
RECLAIM THE LIFE THAT WE LOST
SO MANY YEARS AGO.

07:23.774 --> 07:25.155
YOU HELPED
CLEAR MY NAME.

07:25.155 --> 07:26.867
NOW I'M ALLOWED
TO BE IN THE OPEN,

07:26.867 --> 07:28.659
AND I'VE NEVER
BEEN HAPPIER.

07:28.659 --> 07:31.451
LET ME
DO THE SAME FOR YOU.

07:32.533 --> 07:33.834
HAPPY BIRTHDAY,
BABY.

07:35.125 --> 07:37.247
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKING ]

07:58.398 --> 08:00.941
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

08:00.941 --> 08:01.982
[ SIGHS ] HEY.

08:01.982 --> 08:03.694
NOLAN:
Did you see it?

08:03.694 --> 08:04.945
SEE WHAT?

08:04.945 --> 08:07.487
I JUST SENT YOU THE FIRST SHOT
ACROSS THE BOW.

08:07.487 --> 08:09.239
It's not too late for me
to rescind Margaux's invite,

08:09.239 --> 08:10.991
because that would be
so preferable

08:10.991 --> 08:13.113
to a public smackdown
at my reception that...

08:13.113 --> 08:16.827
ALTHOUGH, THAT GIRL FIGHT
WOULD BE FIERCE.

08:16.827 --> 08:20.961
I'LL HANDLE IT.

08:20.961 --> 08:21.962
[ BUTTON CLICKS ]

08:23.503 --> 08:25.836
[ POP MUSIC PLAYS ]

08:25.836 --> 08:29.720
[ CHUCKLES ]

08:29.720 --> 08:31.682
LADIES,
I AM SO SORRY FOR BEING LATE.

08:31.682 --> 08:33.472
WE WEREN'T SURE
YOU WERE COMING.

08:33.472 --> 08:36.395
WE DIDN'T WANT TO BOTHER YOU
AFTER WHAT YOU'VE BEEN THROUGH.

08:36.395 --> 08:38.438
BUT I GUESS
WHAT DOESN'T KILL YOU...HUH?

08:38.438 --> 08:40.020
[ CHUCKLES ]
SPOKEN WITH THE NAIVETé

08:40.020 --> 08:41.692
OF SOMEONE
WHO'S NEVER KNOWN TRAGEDY.

08:41.692 --> 08:42.693
[ INHALES SHARPLY ]

08:42.693 --> 08:44.565
FOR THAT,
YOU SHOULD BE GRATEFUL.

08:44.565 --> 08:45.986
HOW ARE YOU
HOLDING UP?

08:45.986 --> 08:48.108
I'M FOCUSING
ON THE FUNDRAISER.

08:48.108 --> 08:50.030
AND I HOPE
THAT YOU ALL KNOW

08:50.030 --> 08:51.742
HOW MUCH I APPRECIATE
YOUR PARTICIPATION --

08:51.742 --> 08:54.785
ALL THE CALLS
THAT YOU'RE MAKING AND...

08:56.496 --> 08:58.749
IS SOMETHING ON YOUR MIND,
HEATHER?

08:58.749 --> 09:01.001
[ SIGHS ] I-I WAS...

09:02.502 --> 09:04.334
WE WERE WONDERING,
WHAT DO WE SAY TO SOMEONE

09:04.334 --> 09:06.667
WHO SUGGESTS THAT A
DANIEL GRAYSON FOUNDATION IS --

09:06.667 --> 09:08.719
[ SIGHS ]
OH, WHAT'S THE WORD? --

09:08.719 --> 09:10.631
UH, UNSEEMLY?

09:10.631 --> 09:13.844
UNSEEMLY?

09:13.844 --> 09:15.175
LADIES, I --

09:15.175 --> 09:17.177
EXCUSE ME. VICTORIA.

09:17.177 --> 09:19.349
I BELIEVE
YOU'RE IN MY SEAT.

09:19.349 --> 09:21.311
HAVE WE MET?

09:21.311 --> 09:24.274
NO, NOT OFFICIALLY --
OR UNOFFICIALLY.

09:24.274 --> 09:29.149
BUT I HAVE READ QUITE A BIT
ABOUT YOU -- HAMPTONS ROYALTY.

09:29.149 --> 09:31.822
NATALIE WATERS.
I'M NEW HERE.

09:31.822 --> 09:34.655
YOU MOST CERTAINLY ARE.

09:34.655 --> 09:36.576
WELL, I WAS IN THE MIDDLE
OF A THOUGHT,

09:36.576 --> 09:38.659
BUT IF THIS SEAT
IS THAT IMPORTANT TO YOU...

09:38.659 --> 09:41.121
NO, OF COURSE NOT.
PLEASE, YOU KEEP IT.

09:41.121 --> 09:42.162
ALL RIGHT.

09:42.162 --> 09:44.124
WELL, WHY DON'T YOU
ASK THE HOSTESS

09:44.124 --> 09:45.836
TO SQUEEZE YOU IN
BETWEEN KARENNA AND CELIA?

09:47.417 --> 09:50.210
AND IF YOU DON'T MIND,
WOULD YOU ALSO ASK HER

09:50.210 --> 09:51.882
TO SEND OVER
AN OUNCE OF HACKLEBACK?

09:53.173 --> 09:55.135
WELL,
THAT'S CAVIAR, DEAR.

09:55.135 --> 09:57.307
[ BOTH CHUCKLE SOFTLY ]

09:57.307 --> 09:59.139
[ SIGHS ]

09:59.139 --> 10:01.101
NOW, I'M SURE
THAT WE COULD ALL AGREE

10:01.101 --> 10:02.723
THAT ANYONE
WHO WOULD SUGGEST

10:02.723 --> 10:04.394
THAT MY FUNDRAISER
IS UNSEEMLY

10:04.394 --> 10:06.897
IS NO FRIEND OF OURS
AND UNDESERVING OF OUR TIME.

10:06.897 --> 10:07.898
DON'T YOU THINK?

10:07.898 --> 10:10.490
ABSOLUTELY.

10:10.490 --> 10:12.693
WELL, THEN I LOOK FORWARD
TO SEEING YOU ALL TONIGHT.

10:12.693 --> 10:15.235
[ CHUCKLES ]
TO THE FOUNDATION.

10:17.577 --> 10:20.500
CHEERS.
 CHEERS.
 CHEERS.
 CHEERS.

10:20.500 --> 10:22.582
IF YOU WANT TO GET YOUR SHOES
SHINED BEFORE THE CEREMONY,

10:22.582 --> 10:23.834
I'M GONNA BE
DROPPING MINE OFF.

10:23.834 --> 10:25.545
DID YOU TAKE A BRICK TO THE HEAD
OR SOMETHING?

10:25.545 --> 10:27.007
I SAID
I'M NOT GOING.

10:27.007 --> 10:28.168
IT'S NOT A REQUEST.

10:28.168 --> 10:30.050
ALL RIGHT,
CHIEF TOLD ME TO --

10:30.050 --> 10:32.592
WHAT, TO SLAP SOME SENSE
INTO ME?

10:32.592 --> 10:34.424
YOU'RE COMFORTABLE
WITH ALL THIS. I'M NOT.

10:34.424 --> 10:36.887
HEY, THIS HASN'T EXACTLY BEEN
A CAKEWALK FOR ME, EITHER.

10:36.887 --> 10:39.099
I'M JUST TRYING TO
GET THROUGH IT THE BEST I CAN.

10:39.099 --> 10:41.521
AS YOU SHOULD, BUT YOU DON'T
SEE ME TELLING YOU WHAT TO DO.

10:41.521 --> 10:42.853
NO, I DON'T SEE YOU
TELLING ME ANYTHING.

10:43.814 --> 10:44.895
WHAT'S GOING ON
WITH YOU?

10:44.895 --> 10:46.146
ALL I KNOW IS,

10:46.146 --> 10:47.898
IF ONE MORE PERSON
PUTS A MICROPHONE IN MY FACE,

10:47.898 --> 10:49.900
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT THE HELL I'M GONNA SAY.

10:51.111 --> 10:53.153
BUT THE ICE SCULPTURE'S
ALL SCULPTED.

10:53.153 --> 10:54.534
NOW YOU
DON'T WANT IT?

10:54.534 --> 10:55.986
LOOK,
I WILL PAY FOR IT.

10:55.986 --> 10:57.577
I AM
CANCELING EVERYTHING.

10:57.577 --> 10:59.329
PLEASE HAVE THEM
TAKE IT AWAY.

10:59.329 --> 11:02.122
EXCEPT FOR THE CHAMPAGNE,
WHICH I'M GOING TO NEED --

11:02.122 --> 11:03.333
OKAY.
 IMMEDIATELY.

11:03.333 --> 11:05.085
UH, MARIA,
CAN WE HAVE A MOMENT?

11:05.085 --> 11:06.086
YES.
 [ SIGHS ]

11:06.086 --> 11:07.878
HONEY? DARLING?
YIN TO MY YANG?

11:07.878 --> 11:08.879
[ SIGHS ]

11:08.879 --> 11:10.590
YOU'RE CANCELING
THE RECEPTION?

11:10.590 --> 11:12.843
IT'S A LITTLE LATE
TO BE GETTING COLD FEET.

11:12.843 --> 11:14.504
I MEAN,
WE'RE ALREADY MARRIED.

11:14.504 --> 11:16.847
YEAH, WELL, NOT FOR LONG,
IF MAMA HAS HER WAY.

11:16.847 --> 11:21.221
WHATEVER SHE'S THREATENING,
WE'LL FIND A WAY AROUND IT.

11:21.221 --> 11:23.764
IS THERE A WAY
AROUND MURDER?

11:27.017 --> 11:30.150
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

11:30.150 --> 11:33.523
OKAY,
REMEMBER WHEN I TOLD YOU

11:33.523 --> 11:35.075
I THOUGHT
THERE WAS MORE TO DADDY'S DEATH

11:35.075 --> 11:37.487
THAN JUST
HIS DRINKING?

11:37.487 --> 11:40.080
MAMA SAID
I KILLED HIM, NOLAN.

11:40.080 --> 11:42.162
[ SIGHS ]

11:42.162 --> 11:43.493
AND I THINK
SHE MIGHT BE RIGHT.

11:43.493 --> 11:44.745
THINK?

11:44.745 --> 11:46.827
THAT SEEMS LIKE SOMETHING
YOU MIGHT REMEMBER.

11:46.827 --> 11:47.828
WELL, I DON'T KNOW.

11:47.828 --> 11:49.209
I MEAN,
I WAS JUST 13

11:49.209 --> 11:51.671
WHEN HE FELL TO HIS DEATH
FROM THE STAIRS.

11:51.671 --> 11:52.833
AND YOU KNOW THAT --

11:52.833 --> 11:55.545
THAT'S AROUND THE TIME
I STARTED TO LOSE MY MIND.

11:55.545 --> 11:58.678
LYMAN -- HE SHOWED ME
THIS POLICE REPORT,

11:58.678 --> 12:01.181
AND IT SAYS
THAT I PUSHED HIM.

12:01.181 --> 12:03.553
WELL, MAMA HAD HER JUDGE FRIEND
BURY IT TO PROTECT ME,

12:03.553 --> 12:06.146
BUT NOW IF
I DON'T SIGN THE CONSERVATORSHIP

12:06.146 --> 12:07.347
BACK OVER TO HER --

12:07.347 --> 12:09.109
SHE'S GONNA TELL
THE WORLD?

12:09.109 --> 12:10.480
[ SIGHS ]

12:10.480 --> 12:12.062
LOOK,
IS THERE ANYTHING

12:12.062 --> 12:14.734
YOU CAN REMEMBER
FROM THAT NIGHT -- ANYTHING?

12:14.734 --> 12:21.361
I REMEMBER
STANDING OVER HIS BODY, CRYING.

12:21.361 --> 12:23.864
THAT'S ALL.

12:23.864 --> 12:26.076
BUT THAT REPORT
SAYS I DID A WHOLE LOT MORE,

12:26.076 --> 12:28.038
AND THERE'S FORENSIC WHATSITS,
AND I --

12:28.038 --> 12:29.169
RED, RED, RED.

12:29.169 --> 12:32.002
[ SIGHS ]

12:32.002 --> 12:36.086
LOOK, YOU MAY BE A LITTLE CRAZY,
BUT THIS DOESN'T ADD UP.

12:36.086 --> 12:38.929
I PROMISED I'D FREE YOU
FROM YOUR MOTHER'S CONTROL,

12:38.929 --> 12:40.380
AND THAT
STILL STANDS.

12:40.380 --> 12:41.882
I'M GONNA GET
SOME ANSWERS.

12:41.882 --> 12:44.975
I JUST NEED YOU
TO TRUST ME, OKAY?

12:44.975 --> 12:46.686
[ SNIFFLES ]

12:47.687 --> 12:50.480
I GAVE YOU
THE BENEFIT OF THE DOUBT,

12:50.480 --> 12:53.563
BUT YOUR RAG MADE IT CLEAR
THAT YOU DON'T DESERVE IT.

12:53.563 --> 12:54.774
I AM THE C.E.O.

12:54.774 --> 12:58.028
OF THE FIFTH-LARGEST MEDIA
CONGLOMERATE IN THE WORLD.

12:58.028 --> 13:01.201
DO YOU REALLY THINK I KNOW
WHAT'S BEING REPORTED

13:01.201 --> 13:03.904
IN EVERY SINGLE ONE
OF MY PUBLICATIONS?

13:03.904 --> 13:06.326
YOU DIDN'T KNOW.
THAT'S YOUR PLAY?

13:06.326 --> 13:09.039
TELL ME THIS --
WHAT ARE PEOPLE TO THINK

13:09.039 --> 13:11.171
WHEN THEY SEE YOU
AND DAVID CLARKE TOGETHER?

13:11.171 --> 13:14.004
PERHAPS THE OCCASIONAL

13:14.004 --> 13:16.626
DISTASTEFUL BUT HONEST MISTAKE
OF A MAGAZINE

13:16.626 --> 13:19.509
IS THE PRICE OF ADMISSION
WHEN YOU WEAR TWO MASKS.

13:19.509 --> 13:21.011
IS THAT A THREAT?

13:21.011 --> 13:24.134
IT'S SIMPLY THE WORLD
YOU'VE CHOSEN TO LIVE IN.

13:24.134 --> 13:25.515
MARGAUX,
I HOPE YOU KNOW

13:25.515 --> 13:28.018
THAT I NEVER WANTED
ANY OF THIS TO HAPPEN TO DANIEL.

13:28.018 --> 13:29.189
REALLY?

13:29.189 --> 13:32.312
BECAUSE IT SEEMS TO ME
YOU PUT THOSE WHEELS IN MOTION

13:32.312 --> 13:34.814
THE MOMENT
YOU GOT TO THE HAMPTONS,

13:34.814 --> 13:37.197
WITH LIES I'M NOW
FULLY AWARE OF.

13:40.991 --> 13:44.995
YOU NEED TO REMEMBER THE SECRETS
I HAVE ABOUT YOUR FATHER --

13:44.995 --> 13:46.366
ENOUGH TO SINK YOU

13:46.366 --> 13:50.000
AND THE FIFTH-LARGEST MEDIA
CONGLOMERATE IN THE WORLD.

13:50.000 --> 13:52.412
THEN YOU HAVE
MY ASSURANCE

13:52.412 --> 13:56.836
THAT MY PUBLICATIONS WILL
STEER CLEAR OF YOU AND YOURS.

13:56.836 --> 13:59.960
AND WHY SHOULD I
BELIEVE YOU?

13:59.960 --> 14:03.513
BECAUSE THE MAN I LOVED
DIED SAVING YOU.

14:03.513 --> 14:06.846
AND I WILL NOT
DISHONOR HIS LAST ACTIONS

14:06.846 --> 14:08.848
BY GOING AGAINST
HIS WISHES.

14:11.892 --> 14:13.233
BUT, EMILY...

14:13.233 --> 14:18.148
YOU DO KNOW I DO NOT CONTROL
EVERY NEWS OUTLET IN THE WORLD.

14:18.148 --> 14:21.691
SOONER OR LATER,
THE TRUTH WILL COME OUT.

14:21.691 --> 14:23.533
YOU HANDLE
YOUR OWN EMPIRE.

14:23.533 --> 14:25.195
I'LL WORRY
ABOUT MYSELF.

14:33.914 --> 14:35.956
YOU PROMISED ME
QUICK RESULTS.

14:35.956 --> 14:37.167
WHERE ARE THEY?

14:37.167 --> 14:40.300
I EXPECTED MORE FROM YOU
THAN SCHOOLYARD-GOSSIP ITEMS.

14:40.300 --> 14:42.212
I CAN TRY
CASTING A WIDER NET.

14:42.212 --> 14:44.714
DO WHATEVER IT TAKES
TO GET ME WHAT I NEED

14:44.714 --> 14:47.097
TO EXPOSE
EMILY THORNE.

14:47.097 --> 14:48.678
I WILL NOT
HAVE DANIEL'S NAME TARNISHED

14:48.678 --> 14:50.010
WHILE HERS
REMAINS CLEAN.

14:54.474 --> 14:55.515
THANKS.

14:55.515 --> 14:57.477
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

15:01.151 --> 15:03.153
YOU KNOW, THEY FROWN ON
DRINKING ALONE IN THIS PLACE.

15:03.153 --> 15:05.825
[ CHUCKLES ]
THANKS FOR MEETING ME.

15:05.825 --> 15:08.368
I WASN'T SURE
IF YOU'D HAVE TIME,

15:08.368 --> 15:09.789
WHAT WITH ALL
THE TV INTERVIEWS.

15:09.789 --> 15:10.991
I'M NOT GONNA LIE --

15:10.991 --> 15:12.492
I DID HAVE TO CANCEL
AN APPEARANCE ON "THE VIEW."

15:12.492 --> 15:14.664
BUT YOU CALLED.
IT SOUNDED SERIOUS.

15:14.664 --> 15:15.996
IT'S JACK, RIGHT?

15:15.996 --> 15:19.209
I REALLY HOPE HE GETS
THROUGH ALL THIS THE RIGHT WAY.

15:19.209 --> 15:20.840
GETS THROUGH WHAT?

15:20.840 --> 15:23.463
IS JACK
NOT WHY YOU CALLED?

15:23.463 --> 15:26.506
NO, BUT NOW
THAT YOU BROUGHT IT UP, TELL ME.

15:26.506 --> 15:29.970
IT'S JUST THE AFTERMATH OF THIS
WHOLE MALCOLM BLACK THING --

15:29.970 --> 15:32.012
THE ATTENTION
AND THE SPOTLIGHT.

15:32.012 --> 15:33.553
GUY JUST
SEEMS TORTURED.

15:35.355 --> 15:37.817
JACK TENDS
TO KEEP THINGS INSIDE.

15:37.817 --> 15:39.479
YEAH, WELL,
I'M A LITTLE WORRIED.

15:39.479 --> 15:41.651
WHAT HAPPENS WHEN HE RUNS OUT
OF SPACE IN THERE?

15:45.195 --> 15:47.827
BUT THAT'S
NOT WHY YOU CALLED.

15:50.030 --> 15:51.571
I NEED YOUR ADVICE.

15:51.571 --> 15:54.334
THAT I CAN DO.

15:54.334 --> 15:57.457
I FIGURED THAT YOU WERE SOMEONE
IMPARTIAL I COULD TALK TO.

15:57.457 --> 15:58.748
WELL,
THAT'S WRONG.

15:58.748 --> 16:00.540
I AM PARTIAL.

16:00.540 --> 16:02.252
[ CHUCKLES SOFTLY ]

16:02.252 --> 16:04.544
BUT LET'S --
LET'S PRETEND I'M NOT.

16:04.544 --> 16:05.845
SO, GO ON.

16:08.548 --> 16:11.261
I BECAME EMILY THORNE
TO CLEAR MY FATHER'S NAME.

16:11.261 --> 16:14.684
AND NOW THAT I HAVE,
I'M DONE.

16:14.684 --> 16:17.727
MY FATHER
SEEMS TO WANT ME TO...

16:17.727 --> 16:20.560
JUST GO BACK
TO BEING AMANDA.

16:20.560 --> 16:24.524
BUT YOU'RE HAVING A HARD TIME
LETTING GO OF EMILY.

16:24.524 --> 16:26.486
WHEN I WORKED
UNDERCOVER --

16:26.486 --> 16:28.368
REALLY
WITH THE UNDERCOVER THING AGAIN?

16:28.368 --> 16:29.449
[ BOTH CHUCKLE ]

16:29.449 --> 16:30.990
YOU KNOW,
EXAMINE YOUR SUBCONSCIOUS.

16:30.990 --> 16:34.164
IS THAT STORY
NOT WHY YOU CAME TO ME?

16:34.164 --> 16:36.496
LET'S PRETEND
THAT IT IS.

16:36.496 --> 16:39.579
SO, I WAS UNDERCOVER
FOR SIX MONTHS.

16:39.579 --> 16:42.252
AND YOU'VE BEEN EMILY
FOR...

16:42.252 --> 16:44.044
11 YEARS.

16:44.044 --> 16:47.006
RIGHT.
SO A LITTLE DIFFERENT.

16:47.006 --> 16:49.839
BUT THERE'S YOUR ANSWER.

16:49.839 --> 16:51.341
ALL RIGHT,
THE LONGER THAT YOU'RE UNDER,

16:51.341 --> 16:53.053
THE MORE THE COVER
BECOMES A PART OF WHO YOU ARE,

16:53.053 --> 16:55.395
AND THEN
THE HARDER IT IS

16:55.395 --> 16:57.016
TO GET BACK TO THAT PERSON
YOU WANT TO BE.

16:57.016 --> 16:59.309
UM, SEE,
THAT'S THE THING --

16:59.309 --> 17:02.232
I NEVER INTENDED
TO BE AMANDA AGAIN.

17:02.232 --> 17:04.644
THERE WAS
NOTHING LEFT THERE.

17:04.644 --> 17:08.818
I WAS GONNA CLEAR MY FATHER'S
NAME AND...DISAPPEAR,

17:08.818 --> 17:13.031
THEN LEAVE EMILY THORNE BEHIND,
START OVER AS SOMEONE NEW.

17:14.114 --> 17:16.035
WELL,
DON'T MAKE ME DO THAT.

17:16.035 --> 17:18.117
DO WHAT?

17:18.117 --> 17:21.421
IMAGINE A WORLD
WITHOUT EMILY THORNE.

17:23.002 --> 17:25.003
[ CHUCKLES SOFTLY ]

17:26.876 --> 17:28.758
[ CELLPHONE CHIMES ]

17:34.053 --> 17:35.555
SORRY.

17:35.555 --> 17:37.307
IT'S OKAY.
I GET IT.

17:37.307 --> 17:39.769
EMILY THORNE'S WORK
IS NEVER DONE.

17:39.769 --> 17:43.813
BUT IF EVER IT IS...
I'M AROUND.

17:56.156 --> 17:57.747
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

17:57.747 --> 18:01.371
OH, NO.
DID I GET THE TIME WRONG?

18:01.371 --> 18:04.003
UH, WE WERE
JUST ABOUT WRAP UP,

18:04.003 --> 18:07.337
BUT THERE ARE A FEW PIECES
STILL AVAILABLE.

18:07.337 --> 18:09.509
OH, WE'VE MET.

18:09.509 --> 18:11.171
AT THE BEACH CLUB
EARLIER TODAY.

18:11.171 --> 18:12.512
YES. NATALIE.
 MM-HMM.

18:12.512 --> 18:13.553
YOU WERE THE ONE --

18:13.553 --> 18:14.634
WHOSE CHAMPAGNE
YOU DRANK.

18:14.634 --> 18:16.346
[ BOTH CHUCKLE ]

18:16.346 --> 18:19.429
NO, I WAS ABOUT TO SAY
WHO'S NEW TO THE AREA.

18:19.429 --> 18:22.432
THAT, TOO.
MAY I?

18:22.432 --> 18:23.683
YES.

18:30.280 --> 18:32.031
YOU SEE
ANYTHING YOU LIKE?

18:32.031 --> 18:35.155
[ CHUCKLES ]

18:35.155 --> 18:37.157
I'M NOT
MUCH INTO THE MODERN.

18:37.157 --> 18:39.949
I'M MORE
OF A FAN OF HISTORY --

18:39.949 --> 18:44.504
LIKE THE 16th-CENTURY FRENCH
COURT I WITNESSED AT LUNCH.

18:44.504 --> 18:47.337
THAT WASN'T JUST ANY SEAT
I TOOK --

18:47.337 --> 18:50.250
MORE LIKE A QUEEN'S THRONE
AT THE HEAD OF THE TABLE,

18:50.250 --> 18:51.631
SURROUNDED BY HER PAWNS.

18:51.631 --> 18:53.553
MM, WELL,
THAT'S A FASCINATING THEORY.

18:53.553 --> 18:54.554
ARE YOU A PROFESSOR?

18:54.554 --> 18:55.845
[ LAUGHS ]

18:55.845 --> 18:58.888
MORE LIKE, UM, AN INTERESTED
OBSERVER ON A FIELD TRIP.

19:00.470 --> 19:04.604
NOT MUCH OF A TURNOUT --
NOT EVEN FROM YOUR FRIENDS.

19:04.604 --> 19:07.647
AND AM I TO BELIEVE THAT
YOU PERSUADED THEM NOT TO COME?

19:07.647 --> 19:10.530
NO. [ SCOFFS ]

19:10.530 --> 19:13.863
THAT WOULD MEAN THAT THEY'RE
EITHER A VERY SUGGESTIBLE LOT,

19:13.863 --> 19:17.987
OR THE GRAYSON NAME NO LONGER
COMMANDS THE SAME FEAR,

19:17.987 --> 19:23.122
AWE, AND RESPECT
IT ONCE DID.

19:24.043 --> 19:25.705
IT'S NOT EASY
BEING QUEEN --

19:25.705 --> 19:28.958
I MEAN,
IF YOU BELIEVE YOUR HISTORY.

19:28.958 --> 19:30.500
[ SIGHS ]

19:30.500 --> 19:33.052
GOOD LUCK
WITH THE FOUNDATION.

19:38.388 --> 19:39.509
[ DOOR OPENS ]

19:43.182 --> 19:45.355
HEY.
 HEY.

19:45.355 --> 19:46.806
I WAS HOPING
YOU'D BE HERE.

19:46.806 --> 19:48.608
WELL, IT'S YOUR LUCKY DAY,
YOU KNOW?

19:48.608 --> 19:50.019
I'M GIVING OUT
DOOR PRIZES.

19:50.019 --> 19:53.653
[ CHUCKLES ]

19:53.653 --> 19:54.984
I HEARD THEY'RE
GIVING YOU A MEDAL TOMORROW.

19:54.984 --> 19:56.316
YEAH.

19:56.316 --> 19:59.028
THEY'RE TRYING.

20:01.701 --> 20:03.162
WOULD YOU TAKE IT?

20:03.162 --> 20:05.705
UH, IT'S NOT A PROBLEM
THAT I'M LIKELY TO HAVE.

20:05.705 --> 20:08.418
THEY DON'T HAND THEM OUT
FOR THE THINGS I'VE DONE.

20:08.418 --> 20:10.710
WE'VE DONE
THE SAME THINGS.

20:10.710 --> 20:12.672
WE'VE COVERED UP KILLINGS.

20:12.672 --> 20:15.174
YEAH,
BUT CONRAD WAS UNARMED.

20:15.174 --> 20:16.336
BUT HE DESTROYED
COUNTLESS LIVES.

20:16.336 --> 20:17.337
KATE DIDN'T --
 STOP IT.

20:17.337 --> 20:19.549
DON'T DO THAT
TO YOURSELF.

20:21.140 --> 20:24.764
I TOOK SOMEONE'S LIFE,
DAVID.

20:24.764 --> 20:27.106
YEAH, YOU KNOW
WHAT ELSE YOU DID?

20:27.106 --> 20:29.188
YOU SAVED
MY DAUGHTER'S LIFE.

20:29.188 --> 20:32.061
[ CHUCKLES SOFTLY ]

20:32.061 --> 20:33.983
I DID THAT?

20:33.983 --> 20:36.316
YEP.
YOU SAVED MINE, TOO.

20:36.316 --> 20:40.450
SO...LIKE IT OR NOT,
YOU'RE A HERO.

20:42.492 --> 20:46.205
THEN WHY
CAN'T I LIVE WITH IT?

20:46.205 --> 20:47.537
[ SIGHS ]

20:47.537 --> 20:50.870
WHY DO I
FEEL LIKE A LIAR?

20:50.870 --> 20:52.632
WELL, YOU ARE.
YOU'RE THAT, TOO.

20:52.632 --> 20:55.174
IT'S JUST THAT ONE THING
HAS NOTHING WITH THE OTHER.

20:56.255 --> 20:58.257
I WISH
I COULD BELIEVE THAT.

20:58.257 --> 21:01.301
I WISH YOU COULD, TOO,
BECAUSE IF YOU CAN'T, THEN
SOMETHING'S GOT TO GIVE.

21:11.150 --> 21:14.273
UM...
 NO, IT'S OKAY.

21:14.273 --> 21:15.985
EMILY'S GOING TO USE
A TECHNIQUE

21:15.985 --> 21:19.699
TO HELP YOU UNCOVER THE MEMORY
OF THE NIGHT YOUR FATHER DIED.

21:19.699 --> 21:22.952
AND WHERE DID SHE LEARN
THIS TECHNIQUE?

21:22.952 --> 21:25.325
JAPAN.

21:25.325 --> 21:28.498
TRUST ME,
IT'S VERY EFFECTIVE...AND SAFE.

21:28.498 --> 21:29.999
[ CHUCKLES ]

21:29.999 --> 21:31.831
[ SIGHS ]

21:35.335 --> 21:38.087
THE BRAIN ALLOWS US
TO ACCESS TRAUMA

21:38.087 --> 21:41.421
WHEN WE FACE
THE SAME EMOTIONS --

21:41.421 --> 21:45.595
FEAR AND DANGER.

21:45.595 --> 21:47.727
GIVE ME YOUR HAND.

21:56.646 --> 21:58.147
JUST FOCUS
ON THE BLADE.

21:58.147 --> 22:00.149
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

22:04.494 --> 22:06.576
DON'T LOOK AT ME.

22:11.911 --> 22:13.913
FOCUS ON
YOUR BREATHING...

22:13.913 --> 22:18.217
THE BLADE...

22:18.217 --> 22:22.051
THE FEAR,
THE DANGER.

22:22.051 --> 22:24.093
FOCUS ON THAT NIGHT.

22:25.385 --> 22:26.556
WHAT DO YOU SEE?

22:26.556 --> 22:28.137
Nothing.

22:28.137 --> 22:29.599
WHAT DO YOU SEE,
LOUISE?

22:30.730 --> 22:32.972
I'M AFRAID.

22:32.972 --> 22:35.354
WHY?

22:36.896 --> 22:39.479
DADDY!
 AAH! AAH!

22:39.479 --> 22:42.321
WHAT DID YOU DO?
WHAT DID YOU DO?!

22:43.483 --> 22:46.155
[ GASPS ]

22:46.155 --> 22:48.157
[ INHALES SHARPLY ]
DID YOU REMEMBER, LOUISE?

22:52.752 --> 22:54.414
I DIDN'T DO IT.

22:54.414 --> 22:55.585
[ SIGHS ]

22:57.046 --> 22:59.128
I DIDN'T DO IT.

23:02.842 --> 23:03.843
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

23:03.843 --> 23:05.465
HEY.

23:05.465 --> 23:07.767
HEY.
WHAT'S UP?

23:07.767 --> 23:09.268
WELL,
YOU DIDN'T RETURN MY CALLS,

23:09.268 --> 23:11.390
SO I THOUGHT I'D COME BY,
MAKE SURE YOU'RE OKAY.

23:11.390 --> 23:14.183
I'M FINE.

23:14.183 --> 23:16.816
LOOK, JACK, I KNOW IT'S HARD
KEEPING ALL OF THIS TO YOURSELF,

23:16.816 --> 23:18.818
ESPECIALLY WHEN THE WHOLE WORLD
IS INSISTING

23:18.818 --> 23:20.109
THAT YOU TELL A STORY
THAT'S NOT --

23:20.109 --> 23:21.360
I'M NOT LOSING SLEEP

23:21.360 --> 23:23.693
OVER WHAT THE REST OF THE WORLD
THINKS ABOUT ME.

23:23.693 --> 23:26.025
I KILLED AN FBI AGENT --
A BAD ONE, BUT STILL --

23:26.025 --> 23:27.286
AND WE LIED
ABOUT IT.

23:27.286 --> 23:28.868
WE CONSPIRED
TO HIDE HER BODY,

23:28.868 --> 23:31.701
AND NOW EVERY TIME
I'M ASKED ABOUT IT,

23:31.701 --> 23:34.083
I-I GO THROUGH IT
ALL OVER AGAIN.

23:34.083 --> 23:36.415
THEY WILL STOP --
EVENTUALLY.

23:36.415 --> 23:37.877
YES, BUT I STILL HAVE TO LIVE
WITH WHAT I'VE DONE.

23:39.459 --> 23:40.750
WHAT ARE YOU
REALLY DOING HERE?

23:40.750 --> 23:43.132
I TOLD YOU
I WAS WORRIED.

23:43.132 --> 23:44.173
ABOUT ME?

23:44.173 --> 23:45.424
OR THAT I MIGHT, UH,
MIGHT BLOW A FUSE

23:45.424 --> 23:47.176
AND TELL ONE OF THOSE CAMERA
CREWS EVERYTHING I'VE DONE?

23:47.176 --> 23:48.848
JACK.

23:48.848 --> 23:50.429
I'M RUNNING LATE.

23:50.429 --> 23:53.262
CAN'T KEEP
THE MAYOR WAITING.

23:53.262 --> 23:55.855
APPARENTLY,
HE HATES THAT.

23:55.855 --> 23:57.477
[ CAR DOOR CLOSES ]

23:57.477 --> 23:58.648
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

24:01.360 --> 24:02.862
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

24:02.862 --> 24:06.025
NOLAN.
 SASHA. KIERSTEN.

24:06.025 --> 24:08.277
HAMPTONS HELLIONS.

24:08.277 --> 24:10.530
UM,
BEHAVE YOURSELF.

24:10.530 --> 24:12.371
HEY,
MAN OF THE HOUR.

24:12.371 --> 24:14.203
[ SPEAKS INDISTINCTLY ]
 YEAH. GREAT PARTY.

24:14.203 --> 24:15.454
OH, MY.

24:15.454 --> 24:19.669
WELL, VERY DASHING
FOR A FUTURE EX-SON-IN-LAW.

24:19.669 --> 24:21.420
WHERE'S THE BLUSHING BRIDE?

24:21.420 --> 24:24.133
YOU SOUTHERN WOMEN
WON'T BE RUSHED.

24:24.133 --> 24:26.005
SHE'LL BE DOWN
ANY MOMENT.

24:26.005 --> 24:27.507
WELL,
WHEN SHE DOES GRACE US,

24:27.507 --> 24:30.349
I WANT TO MAKE SURE THAT LOUISE
SAYS HELLO TO JUDGE MILLER,

24:30.349 --> 24:31.350
A DEAR FAMILY FRIEND.

24:31.350 --> 24:32.431
AH,
JUDGE MILLER.

24:32.431 --> 24:35.184
YOUR REPUTATION
PRECEDES YOU, SIR.

24:35.184 --> 24:36.806
I WOULD SAY
IT'S A PLEASURE,

24:36.806 --> 24:38.477
BUT MY MOTHER TAUGHT ME
NOT TO LIE.

24:38.477 --> 24:41.440
NOW,
IF YOU'LL EXCUSE ME...

24:41.440 --> 24:43.272
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

24:43.272 --> 24:44.654
YOUR HONOR.
 MM.

24:44.654 --> 24:46.235
YOU SHOULD TAKE A GANDER
AT THE ICE-SCULPTURE GARDEN.

24:46.235 --> 24:47.316
I'VE NEVER
SEEN ANYTHING LIKE IT.

24:47.316 --> 24:49.408
OH,
SOUNDS DECADENT.

24:49.408 --> 24:50.990
I BELIEVE I WILL.

24:53.322 --> 24:54.824
MOM,
ARE WE SURE ABOUT THIS?

24:54.824 --> 24:56.205
LOUISE HAS BEEN THROUGH
QUITE A BIT.

24:56.205 --> 24:57.496
THERE'S NO GUARANTEE
THIS WON'T --

24:57.496 --> 24:59.378
SHE'S MY DAUGHTER,
LYMAN.

24:59.378 --> 25:02.211
LOUISE WON'T GET HURT
AS LONG AS SHE BEHAVES

25:02.211 --> 25:04.333
AND SIGNS THE CONSERVATORSHIP
BACK OVER TO ME.

25:04.333 --> 25:05.424
[ SIGHS ]

25:05.424 --> 25:06.586
OKAY, WELL,
IF THIS SHIP GOES DOWN,

25:06.586 --> 25:08.007
I WANT YOU
TO TELL ME FIRST.

25:08.007 --> 25:09.839
I'LL NEED TO FIND
ALTERNATE FINANCING.

25:09.839 --> 25:12.341
YOU'LL GET YOUR FUNDING, SON.
TRUST ME.

25:14.343 --> 25:18.978
THIS IS GONNA BE A RUNAWAY BRIDE
OF BIBLICAL PROPORTIONS.

25:20.189 --> 25:23.022
OFFICERS BEN HUNTER
AND JACK PORTER,

25:23.022 --> 25:28.698
FOR BRAVE ACTIONS IN
THE LINE OF DUTY, WE SALUTE YOU.

25:28.698 --> 25:31.530
[ SNIFFLES ]

25:33.072 --> 25:35.284
HOW DOES IT FEEL TO BE
A LOCAL HERO, OFFICER PORTER?

25:35.284 --> 25:37.206
ASK MY PARTNER.

25:37.206 --> 25:40.870
I WAS JUST SITTING SHOTGUN
TO THE BEST COP IN TOWN.

25:40.870 --> 25:42.501
SEE?
WAS THAT SO HARD, PORTER?

25:42.501 --> 25:44.584
WELL,
THE HARD PART'S NEXT.

25:44.584 --> 25:47.466
I NEED TO TALK TO YOU
AFTER THE CEREMONY.

25:47.466 --> 25:50.720
[ APPLAUSE ]

25:50.720 --> 25:52.431
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

25:52.431 --> 25:54.844
HEY.
WHAT'S GOING ON?

25:54.844 --> 25:58.557
LOUISE HAS GONE
"BYE-BYE, BRIDEY,"
BUT SHE LEFT A NOTE.

25:58.557 --> 26:00.059
WHAT?
 [ SIGHS ]

26:00.059 --> 26:03.182
"I DID IT.
I'M SORRY.

26:03.182 --> 26:05.484
I CAN'T
RUIN YOUR LIFE, TOO. LOUISE."

26:05.484 --> 26:07.446
SHE MUST HAVE LIED
ABOUT WHAT SHE REMEMBERED.

26:07.446 --> 26:08.948
SHE COULDN'T FACE ME
OR ANYONE.

26:08.948 --> 26:10.529
WELL, SHE JUST ADMITTED
TO KILLING SOMEONE.

26:10.529 --> 26:11.691
MAYBE SHE
TURNED HERSELF IN.

26:11.691 --> 26:12.992
UH, NOPE.

26:12.992 --> 26:16.696
SHE'S OUT IN THE BOONIES,
NOT NEAR ANY POLICE STATION.

26:16.696 --> 26:17.867
[ SIGHS ]

26:17.867 --> 26:19.078
I KNOW
EXACTLY WHERE THIS IS.

26:19.078 --> 26:20.329
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]
LET'S GO.

26:20.329 --> 26:21.661
NO, NOLAN,
YOU CAN'T LEAVE.

26:21.661 --> 26:23.252
YOU HAVE
HUNDREDS OF GUESTS HERE

26:23.252 --> 26:24.964
AND A VERY SUSPICIOUS
MOTHER-IN-LAW.

26:24.964 --> 26:26.335
I NEED
TO TALK TO LOUISE.

26:26.335 --> 26:28.377
AND I WILL GET YOU THAT CHANCE,
I PROMISE,

26:28.377 --> 26:31.801
BUT YOU HAVE TO PREPARE YOURSELF
FOR WHAT SHE HAS TO SAY.

26:32.972 --> 26:36.175
WHEN YOU FIND HER,
GIVE HER THIS.

26:36.175 --> 26:39.428
SHE'LL COME BACK.

26:39.428 --> 26:41.310
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

26:41.310 --> 26:43.482
[ CHUCKLES ] MS. WATERS.

26:43.482 --> 26:45.484
NEW TO TOWN
AND ALREADY SOMEONE'S PLUS-ONE.

26:45.484 --> 26:47.817
SUCH A WARM
AND EMBRACING COMMUNITY.

26:47.817 --> 26:48.818
OH.

26:48.818 --> 26:50.189
I'M SO RELIEVED
YOU'RE ALL OKAY.

26:50.189 --> 26:52.191
I WAS AFRAID A PACK OF
WILD ANIMALS HAD GOTTEN TO YOU,

26:52.191 --> 26:53.993
CONSIDERING YOUR NO-SHOWS
LAST NIGHT.

26:53.993 --> 26:55.945
UH, VICTORIA,
I AM SO SORRY.

26:55.945 --> 26:57.616
VICTORIA, BOBBY HAD
A TERRIBLE STOMACH BUG.
 OH, NO. I UNDERSTAND.

26:57.616 --> 26:59.909
AH.
 [ CHUCKLES ]

26:59.909 --> 27:02.081
HEATHER...
AFTER I SUPPORTED YOU

27:02.081 --> 27:05.835
THROUGH YOUR HUSBAND'S DALLIANCE
WITH THAT POOL BOY LAST SUMMER,

27:05.835 --> 27:07.336
I THOUGHT
THERE MIGHT BE A GOOD REASON

27:07.336 --> 27:09.508
FOR YOUR ABSENCE
LAST NIGHT.

27:09.508 --> 27:10.920
EXCUSE ME.
 NO, PLEASE STAY.

27:10.920 --> 27:12.341
[ CHUCKLES ]

27:12.341 --> 27:13.843
[ SIGHS ]

27:13.843 --> 27:16.175
OH,
THAT WAS INDISCREET.

27:16.175 --> 27:19.518
THE POINT I WAS TRYING TO MAKE
IS THIS...

27:19.518 --> 27:23.853
A FRIEND
IS LIKE A BUSINESS.

27:23.853 --> 27:27.226
INVESTING IN THE WRONG ONE
ALWAYS PROVES COSTLY.

27:27.226 --> 27:30.479
AND LIKE HEATHER,
I'M SURE THAT YOU WOULD ALL

27:30.479 --> 27:33.152
WANT ME
TO KEEP YOUR SECRETS SECRET.

27:33.152 --> 27:37.036
FOR EXAMPLE, SUPPOSE ONE
OF MY DEAR FRIENDS' HUSBANDS

27:37.036 --> 27:40.780
WAS SLEEPING WITH SOMEONE ELSE
IN THIS VERY CIRCLE

27:40.780 --> 27:44.543
OR THAT ANOTHER WAS USING
A CONTROLLED WHITE POWDER

27:44.543 --> 27:47.707
AS A WEIGHT-LOSS SUPPLEMENT.

27:47.707 --> 27:50.589
BUT THIS REAL FRIEND
ENSURES THAT YOUR INDISCRETIONS

27:50.589 --> 27:52.051
REMAIN CONFIDENTIAL

27:52.051 --> 27:55.965
IN RETURN FOR YOUR SUPPORT OF
THE DANIEL GRAYSON FOUNDATION.

27:55.965 --> 28:00.139
SO WHATEVER YOU WERE PLANNING ON
DONATING LAST NIGHT, DOUBLE IT.

28:00.139 --> 28:02.471
ANYTHING LESS
WOULD BE UNSEEMLY,

28:02.471 --> 28:03.642
DON'T YOU THINK?

28:14.734 --> 28:16.695
[ KEYBOARD CLACKING ]

28:16.695 --> 28:19.368
EXCUSE ME.
CAN I HELP YOU?

28:19.368 --> 28:21.700
ANNA BISHOP, NEW YORK STATE
OFFICE OF MENTAL HEALTH.

28:21.700 --> 28:22.872
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

28:22.872 --> 28:24.824
I'M HERE TO DO A SPOT CHECK
OF YOUR FACILITY.

28:24.824 --> 28:26.665
UH, I'D BE HAPPY
TO SHOW YOU AROUND.

28:26.665 --> 28:28.377
AND ABANDON
THE ADMISSION DESK

28:28.377 --> 28:30.209
AT A SECURE
PSYCHIATRIC FACILITY?

28:30.209 --> 28:33.042
YOU JUST FAILED
YOUR FIRST TEST.

28:33.042 --> 28:35.384
READ THE PROTOCOL AND
BUZZ ME IN -- NOT IN THAT ORDER.

28:35.384 --> 28:40.009
AND I'LL NEED AN UP-TO-DATE
PATIENT LIST, PLEASE.

28:40.009 --> 28:42.511
THANK YOU.

28:46.145 --> 28:48.017
EMILY,
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?!

28:48.017 --> 28:50.189
I'M BRINGING YOU BACK.
 [ DOOR CLOSES ]

28:50.189 --> 28:52.812
NO. I WILL NOT
RUIN NOLAN'S LIFE.

28:52.812 --> 28:55.194
THIS IS
WHERE I DESERVE TO BE.

28:55.194 --> 28:56.485
CLAREMONT PSYCHIATRIC?

28:56.485 --> 28:58.988
THERE ARE VERY FEW PEOPLE
WHO DESERVE TO BE HERE,

28:58.988 --> 29:00.820
AND YOU
DON'T EVEN COME CLOSE.

29:00.820 --> 29:02.862
I LIED TO YOU,
EMILY.

29:02.862 --> 29:04.703
I LIED TO NOLAN.

29:04.703 --> 29:06.786
I KILLED MY FATHER.

29:06.786 --> 29:08.127
YOU'RE RIGHT
ON TWO OUT OF THREE.

29:09.168 --> 29:11.210
IF YOU TOLD US THE TRUTH
ABOUT WHAT YOU REMEMBERED,

29:11.210 --> 29:12.711
WE COULD'VE HELPED YOU.

29:12.711 --> 29:13.963
HOW?

29:13.963 --> 29:16.295
WITH SOME OTHER MAGIC TRICK
YOU LEARNED ON MOUNT FUJI?

29:16.295 --> 29:18.007
[ SIGHS ] NO.

29:20.089 --> 29:22.761
WITH NOLAN'S
WEDDING GIFT.

29:26.685 --> 29:30.810
IT'S THE REAL POLICE REPORT
FROM THE NIGHT YOUR FATHER DIED.

29:30.810 --> 29:33.943
THE ONE YOUR BROTHER SHOWED YOU
WAS FORGED.

29:33.943 --> 29:35.815
YOU DIDN'T PUSH HIM.

29:35.815 --> 29:38.357
WELL,
ARE YOU SURE?

29:38.357 --> 29:40.489
I MEAN, H-HOW DO YOU KNOW
THIS ISN'T THE FORGERY?

29:40.489 --> 29:42.611
BECAUSE NOLAN
MOVED HEAVEN AND EARTH

29:42.611 --> 29:44.573
TO FIND THE BEAT COP
WHO RESPONDED

29:44.573 --> 29:46.665
TO THE SCENE
OF YOUR FATHER'S DEATH.

29:46.665 --> 29:48.577
BUT I DON'T UNDERSTAND.

29:48.577 --> 29:51.170
I REMEMBERED
SEEING HIM FALL.

29:51.170 --> 29:53.502
THAT DOESN'T MEAN
YOU PUSHED HIM.

29:56.625 --> 29:58.337
[ BODY THUDS ]

29:58.337 --> 29:59.338
DADDY!

29:59.338 --> 30:01.841
AAH! AAH!

30:03.342 --> 30:06.846
I WAS TRYING
TO CATCH AHOLD OF HIM.

30:06.846 --> 30:09.138
YOU UNLOCKED THE MEMORY.

30:09.138 --> 30:12.811
I JUST...
WOULDN'T LET MYSELF SEE IT.

30:12.811 --> 30:16.485
[ Voice breaking ] AND MY MOTHER
KNEW THE TRUTH THIS WHOLE TIME?

30:16.485 --> 30:17.566
[ SIGHS ]

30:17.566 --> 30:19.148
SHE HAD THE JUDGE
BURY THE ORIGINAL REPORT

30:19.148 --> 30:21.200
AND CREATE A FALSE ONE
TO USE AGAINST YOU.

30:21.200 --> 30:23.322
HOW COULD NOLAN
HAVE SUCH FAITH IN ME

30:23.322 --> 30:25.154
WHEN I HAD NO FAITH
IN MYSELF?

30:25.154 --> 30:26.946
'CAUSE THAT'S
WHO NOLAN IS.

30:28.617 --> 30:32.331
NOW, LET'S GET YOU BACK
TO YOUR ANXIOUS HUSBAND.

30:32.331 --> 30:35.544
WELL, I GUESS IT'S TRUE
WHAT THEY SAY --

30:35.544 --> 30:38.547
"MARRY THE MAN,
MARRY HIS FRIENDS."

30:38.547 --> 30:39.959
EMILY.

30:41.340 --> 30:43.382
THANK YOU.

30:43.382 --> 30:46.926
[ SIGHS ]

30:46.926 --> 30:49.929
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

30:55.644 --> 30:58.317
WELL [CLEARS THROAT] BARTENDER
SAID HE'D BE RIGHT BACK,

30:58.317 --> 31:01.070
BUT LAST I SAW, HE WAS
HITTING ON THE PEACOCK WRANGLER.

31:01.070 --> 31:02.481
[ BOTH CHUCKLE SOFTLY ]

31:05.074 --> 31:06.865
DANIEL DIED A HERO.

31:08.787 --> 31:11.450
JUST WANTED YOU
TO KNOW THAT.

31:11.450 --> 31:14.793
I'M SORRY
THE REST OF THE WORLD CAN'T.

31:14.793 --> 31:15.995
THANK YOU, JACK.

31:15.995 --> 31:19.338
YOU'RE THE ONLY PERSON
WHO HAS SAID THAT TO ME.

31:21.300 --> 31:24.763
I HEARD YOU GOT A MEDAL
FROM THE MAYOR TODAY.

31:24.763 --> 31:25.965
I DID,
YEAH, YEAH.

31:25.965 --> 31:28.007
AND I LEFT IT,
ALONG WITH MY BADGE AND MY GUN,

31:28.007 --> 31:29.808
ON THE CHIEF'S DESK.

31:29.808 --> 31:31.390
WHAT, YOU QUIT?
WHY?

31:31.390 --> 31:34.013
TURNS OUT BEING A COP JUST
WASN'T THE RIGHT THING FOR ME.

31:34.013 --> 31:35.144
[ SIGHS ]

31:35.144 --> 31:37.977
TOO MANY, UH...
CONFLICTS OF INTEREST.

31:37.977 --> 31:40.319
I COULD'VE TOLD YOU THAT.

31:40.319 --> 31:42.861
[ BOTH CHUCKLE SOFTLY ]

31:45.945 --> 31:48.157
WELL, I DON'T THINK
THIS GUY'S COMING BACK.

31:52.371 --> 31:53.532
OH, UM...

31:53.532 --> 31:55.374
IT'S SODA WATER
WITH A TWIST.

31:55.374 --> 31:58.537
I HEARD
THE GOOD NEWS.

31:58.537 --> 32:01.090
THE WHOLE THING
TERRIFIES ME.

32:01.090 --> 32:03.172
I'D WORRY
IF IT DIDN'T.

32:03.172 --> 32:05.304
[ CHUCKLES ]
BUT I'VE SEEN YOU WITH CARL.

32:05.304 --> 32:06.805
YOU'RE GONNA BE
A NATURAL.

32:07.967 --> 32:10.809
TO YOUR CHILD.

32:10.809 --> 32:14.143
MAY HE OR SHE GROW UP
IN A LESS COMPLICATED WORLD.

32:14.143 --> 32:15.554
THANK YOU,
JACK.

32:17.316 --> 32:20.319
[ PIANO PLAYS,
INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

32:42.001 --> 32:45.174
SINCE YOU'RE WONDERING,
I'M HERE FOR THE BRIDE.

32:45.174 --> 32:46.505
ARE YOU SURE?

32:46.505 --> 32:48.637
I'VE BEEN HONORING
OUR DEAL, DAVID.

32:48.637 --> 32:50.179
WELL,
IT'S A BIG PARTY.

32:50.179 --> 32:53.512
I'M SURE WE CAN PUT A COUPLE
HUNDRED PEOPLE BETWEEN US.

32:55.144 --> 32:57.096
TELL ME SOMETHING.

33:01.150 --> 33:04.653
HAD YOU WALKED IN MY SHOES
20 YEARS AGO,

33:04.653 --> 33:09.028
WOULD YOU HAVE DONE WHAT I DID
TO PROTECT YOUR CHILD?

33:09.028 --> 33:11.240
WELL, I ALREADY DID,
VICTORIA,

33:11.240 --> 33:13.822
WHEN I HAD YOU
TARNISH DANIEL'S NAME.

33:15.494 --> 33:18.037
OH.

33:18.037 --> 33:21.120
BUT YOU ALREADY KNEW THE ANSWER,
DIDN'T YOU?

33:21.120 --> 33:23.332
JUST WANTED
TO HEAR ME SAY IT.

33:23.332 --> 33:27.086
MAYBE I NEEDED TO.

33:35.804 --> 33:38.807
WHAT WITH NEW YORK
BEING SUCH A HUB,

33:38.807 --> 33:40.979
SHE COULD PROBABLY BE ANYWHERE
BY ABOUT NOW.

33:40.979 --> 33:43.021
NEXT TIME, PERHAPS YOU'LL BE
A LITTLE BIT MORE CAREFUL

33:43.021 --> 33:45.484
ABOUT MEDDLING
IN FAMILY BUSINESS, MR. ROSS.

33:47.406 --> 33:51.490
[ GASPS ] LOU-LOU!
OH, THANK HEAVENS, DARLING.

33:51.490 --> 33:53.072
WE WERE ALL
SO WORRIED!

33:53.072 --> 33:54.243
OH, CUT THE CRAP,
MAMA.

33:56.495 --> 33:58.787
I DIDN'T KILL DADDY --
YOU DID.

33:58.787 --> 34:00.038
YOU MURDERED HIM

34:00.038 --> 34:02.211
AND TRIED TO MAKE ME THINK
IT WAS MY FAULT.

34:05.504 --> 34:07.626
WELL, NOW, DARLING,
THAT'S A COLORFUL STORY --

34:07.626 --> 34:11.590
EXACTLY THE KIND OF TALL TALE
YOU HAD A PENCHANT FOR TELLING

34:11.590 --> 34:15.134
BACK AT THE INSTITUTION
BEFORE THEY FIXED YOUR HEAD.

34:16.175 --> 34:18.597
IT'S NO TALL TALE.

34:18.597 --> 34:22.231
I KNOW EXACTLY WHAT HAPPENED
THE NIGHT DADDY DIED.

34:22.231 --> 34:25.023
I WAS IN MY BEDROOM,
AND I HEARD ARGUING.

34:25.023 --> 34:26.275
Penelope:
DON'T YOU EVER --

34:26.275 --> 34:28.065
YOUR JUDGE FORGOT SOMETHING!
 NO, HE DID NOT!

34:28.065 --> 34:29.648
Louise: DADDY FOUND OUT
YOU WERE CHEATING ON HIM...

34:29.648 --> 34:32.110
DON'T YOU LAUGH AT ME!
 ...WITH JUDGE MILLER.

34:32.110 --> 34:33.742
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

34:33.742 --> 34:35.072
[ GRUNTS ]
 AAH!

34:35.072 --> 34:36.495
OHH! OHH!
 DADDY!

34:36.495 --> 34:38.197
I REACHED FOR HIS HAND.

34:38.197 --> 34:41.409
WHAT DID YOU DO,
HUH?

34:41.409 --> 34:43.792
WHAT DID YOU DO?!

34:43.792 --> 34:47.005
Y-YOU...

34:47.005 --> 34:48.627
YOU'VE BEEN LYING ABOUT IT
EVER SINCE.

34:48.627 --> 34:52.591
YOU DRUGGED ME
AND MADE ME THINK I WAS CRAZY,

34:52.591 --> 34:55.804
ALL SO YOU COULD RETAIN CONTROL
OF MY MONEY.

34:56.975 --> 35:01.140
YEAH, WELL, WHO DO YOU THINK
THE COURT IS GOING TO BELIEVE

35:01.140 --> 35:04.313
WHEN THAT POLICE REPORT
IS UNSEALED, HMM --

35:04.313 --> 35:06.485
A PILLAR
OF THE COMMUNITY

35:06.485 --> 35:09.488
OR YOUR OWN
CHRONICALLY MEDICATED SELF?

35:09.488 --> 35:12.491
OH.
WELL, THAT DEPENDS.

35:12.491 --> 35:14.943
WHICH REPORT
ARE YOU REFERRING TO --

35:14.943 --> 35:17.236
YOUR FORGERY...

35:17.236 --> 35:19.498
OR THE ORIGINAL
MY HUSBAND FOUND?

35:25.374 --> 35:27.376
[ SIGHS ]
 LIES.

35:27.376 --> 35:29.378
TURNS OUT
THE FIRST OFFICER ON THE SCENE

35:29.378 --> 35:32.841
RETIRED A WHILE BACK, BUT,
UH, HE NEVER FORGOT THAT NIGHT.

35:32.841 --> 35:35.514
AND HE KEPT
GREAT RECORDS.

35:35.514 --> 35:36.675
THIS IS NOTHING

35:36.675 --> 35:38.967
BUT A LOT OF TYPICAL
YANKEE HOGWASH AND HORSECRAP.

35:38.967 --> 35:41.850
Nolan: OH, JUDGE MILLER,
THAT IS A LOVELY CANE.

35:41.850 --> 35:43.021
ANTIQUE?

35:43.021 --> 35:44.022
[ INHALES SHARPLY ]

35:44.022 --> 35:45.434
YOU MIND
IF I TAKE A CLOSER LOOK?

35:45.434 --> 35:51.440
I CAN SEE WHERE WE ARE
NOT WELCOME HERE, PENELOPE.

35:51.440 --> 35:54.233
I'LL BE IN THE CAR.

36:00.909 --> 36:03.372
SO,
WHAT NOW, LOU-LOU?

36:03.372 --> 36:07.876
GO HOME, MOTHER.

36:07.876 --> 36:11.710
AND IF YOU DARE
STEP OUT OF LINE ONCE,

36:11.710 --> 36:15.294
IF YOU DARE STEP
OUT OF THE STATE OF GEORGIA,

36:15.294 --> 36:16.675
THERE'S A BED
WAITING FOR YOU

36:16.675 --> 36:19.348
AT CLAREMONT
PSYCHIATRIC INSTITUTE.

36:19.348 --> 36:21.640
THANKS FOR COMING,
MOM.

36:21.640 --> 36:23.181
UH,
APOLOGIES IN ADVANCE --

36:23.181 --> 36:26.685
I DON'T THINK WE'LL BE
MAKING IT DOWN FOR THANKSGIVING.

36:32.941 --> 36:34.813
[ BOTH CHUCKLE ]

36:40.319 --> 36:43.322
[ PIANO MUSIC PLAYS,
INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

36:45.874 --> 36:47.085
[ CHUCKLES ]

36:47.085 --> 36:49.207
REMEMBER WE USED TO
DO THIS IN OUR LIVING ROOM,

36:49.207 --> 36:50.539
HARRY NILSSON
PLAYING?

36:50.539 --> 36:53.171
ME STANDING ON YOUR FEET
'CAUSE I COULDN'T KEEP UP,

36:53.171 --> 36:54.713
TELLING YOU
TO STOP SINGING

36:54.713 --> 36:56.174
'CAUSE YOU WERE NO
HARRY NILSSON.

36:56.174 --> 36:57.336
[ BOTH LAUGH ]

36:57.336 --> 37:00.259
YOU WERE
SUCH A HAPPY CHILD, AMANDA.

37:00.259 --> 37:03.141
I WAS.

37:03.141 --> 37:04.643
THAT ENDED
WHEN I WAS 9.

37:04.643 --> 37:06.555
YEAH.

37:06.555 --> 37:09.898
THAT'S WHY
IT'S TIME TO START AGAIN.

37:09.898 --> 37:11.480
I CAN'T DO THIS.

37:11.480 --> 37:13.231
I'M SORRY.

37:13.231 --> 37:16.945
I CAN'T JUST...
BE AMANDA CLARKE.

37:16.945 --> 37:19.318
[ SIGHS ]
DON'T BE UPSET.

37:19.318 --> 37:21.700
I ONLY ASKED
BECAUSE I WANT YOU TO BE HAPPY.

37:21.700 --> 37:24.413
THAT WAS THE LAST TIME
THAT I REMEMBERED YOU WERE.

37:25.994 --> 37:28.246
LOOK AROUND.

37:28.246 --> 37:32.331
I'VE GOT FRIENDS.

37:32.331 --> 37:33.502
I'VE GOT YOU.

37:35.294 --> 37:37.045
TELLING THE WHOLE WORLD
WHO I AM

37:37.045 --> 37:39.588
WOULD JUST
UPEND EVERYONE'S LIVES.

37:39.588 --> 37:43.552
BUT I'M HAPPY
THAT YOU ASKED

37:43.552 --> 37:46.385
BECAUSE I DIDN'T REALIZE
THAT I WAS HAPPY UNTIL YOU DID.

37:46.385 --> 37:47.476
AH.

37:47.476 --> 37:48.597
[ SIGHS ]

37:48.597 --> 37:50.769
NOW WE JUST NEED
TO STAY OUT OF THE TABLOIDS.

37:50.769 --> 37:52.060
YES, YES.

37:52.060 --> 37:53.652
WELL, YOU KNOW, IT ONLY TAKES
ONE GUY TO CHANGE ALL THAT.

37:53.652 --> 37:55.774
[ CHUCKLES ]

37:59.658 --> 38:00.739
[ LAUGHS ]

38:00.739 --> 38:02.030
SO THEN I SAID...

38:02.030 --> 38:03.241
LYMAN.

38:03.241 --> 38:04.823
WHAT ARE YOU
STILL DOING HERE?

38:04.823 --> 38:06.995
[ Voice breaking ]
I FEEL TERRIBLE, LOUISE.

38:06.995 --> 38:09.207
I-I WANT YOU TO -- TO KNOW
I-I WAS NOT AWARE

38:09.207 --> 38:10.669
OF THE FULL EXTENT
OF MOTHER'S DECEIT.

38:10.669 --> 38:11.670
NOW,
YOU MUST BELIEVE ME.

38:11.670 --> 38:13.502
MUST SHE?

38:13.502 --> 38:15.834
YOU THINK I DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE AFTER?

38:15.834 --> 38:18.507
YOU KNOW,
YOU'VE ALWAYS BEEN MAMA'S BOY,

38:18.507 --> 38:20.679
SO MAYBE THIS WILL BE GOOD
FOR YOU --

38:20.679 --> 38:24.803
I AM CUTTING YOU AND
YOUR CAMPAIGN OFF FROM MY MONEY.

38:26.014 --> 38:28.637
PARTY'S OVER,
LYMAN.

38:28.637 --> 38:31.690
AND I BELIEVE
SHE MEANS THAT

38:31.690 --> 38:35.894
BOTH LITERALLY AND...
METAPHORICALLY.

38:38.066 --> 38:40.198
[ JAZZ MUSIC PLAYS ]

38:40.198 --> 38:41.279
THANK YOU.

38:41.279 --> 38:43.241
I CAN'T BELIEVE YOUR GUY
NEVER CAME BACK.

38:43.241 --> 38:44.363
SCREW HIM.

38:44.363 --> 38:46.324
YOU'VE GOT A KNACK.

38:46.324 --> 38:48.867
I DON'T WANT
TO BE FORWARD,

38:48.867 --> 38:50.248
BUT I NEED SOMEONE

38:50.248 --> 38:53.251
FOR THE FELDMAN BAR MITZVAH
NEXT WEEKEND.

38:53.251 --> 38:54.332
ARE YOU FREE?

38:54.332 --> 38:56.254
[ CELLPHONE CHIMES ]

38:59.217 --> 39:00.959
[ CLICKS TONGUE ]

39:00.959 --> 39:02.551
UH [SIGHS]

39:02.551 --> 39:03.592
YOU HAVE TO GO.

39:03.592 --> 39:06.425
I DO.
[ CHUCKLES ]

39:06.425 --> 39:07.386
I'M SORRY.

39:10.178 --> 39:13.181
[ RUSTLING ]

39:45.003 --> 39:47.345
PERHAPS WE GOT OFF
ON THE WRONG FOOT EARLIER?

39:50.268 --> 39:52.641
WELL, DON'T GO
BACKPEDALING NOW, NATALIE.

39:52.641 --> 39:55.183
I WAS JUST BEGINNING
TO ADMIRE YOUR BOLDNESS.

39:55.183 --> 39:58.356
THAT WAS A VERY IMPRESSIVE
DISPLAY EARLIER,

39:58.356 --> 40:01.109
HOW YOU MANAGED
TO MONETIZE SECRETS.

40:01.109 --> 40:03.782
I IMAGINE YOUR FOUNDATION
IS FLUSH.

40:03.782 --> 40:05.193
IT'S ON ITS WAY.

40:05.193 --> 40:06.695
THE GOOD NEWS IS,

40:06.695 --> 40:08.406
THERE ARE STILL
PLENTY OF SECRETS OUT THERE.

40:08.406 --> 40:09.948
EVERYONE HAS THEM.

40:09.948 --> 40:11.870
AND SOONER OR LATER,
I MAY EVEN LEARN YOURS.

40:11.870 --> 40:12.911
HMM.

40:12.911 --> 40:15.033
[ CHUCKLING ]

40:15.033 --> 40:17.746
OH, I SUSPECT
IT WILL BE SOONER.

40:17.746 --> 40:18.747
MM.

40:18.747 --> 40:20.879
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

40:24.503 --> 40:25.544
HELLO.

40:25.544 --> 40:27.345
MAN: [ British accent ]
Mrs. Grayson.

40:27.345 --> 40:29.638
My apologies
for the late call,

40:29.638 --> 40:32.971
but I'm afraid there's been
a death in the family.

40:34.513 --> 40:36.685
YOU'RE GOING TO BE
VERY HAPPY.

40:40.859 --> 40:42.981
Jack: I'M NOT
LOSING ANY SLEEP

40:42.981 --> 40:45.614
OVER WHAT THE REST OF THE WORLD
THINKS ABOUT ME.

40:45.614 --> 40:48.196
I KILLED AN FBI AGENT --
A BAD ONE, BUT STILL --

40:48.196 --> 40:49.658
AND WE LIED
ABOUT IT.

40:49.658 --> 40:51.369
WE CONSPIRED
TO HIDE HER BODY,

40:51.369 --> 40:53.572
AND NOW EVERY TIME
I'M ASKED ABOUT IT --

40:53.572 --> 40:55.243
[ BUTTON CLICKS ]
 WHAT'S THIS?

40:55.243 --> 40:57.375
THE SMOKING GUN
YOU ASKED FOR.

40:57.375 --> 40:59.498
I ASKED FOR EVIDENCE
ON EMILY.

40:59.498 --> 41:01.840
YOU TOLD ME
TO CAST A WIDER NET.

41:01.840 --> 41:04.172
THEY'RE IN
ON THIS THING TOGETHER.

41:04.172 --> 41:06.294
HAS THE PLAN CHANGED?

41:06.294 --> 41:08.086
[ BUTTON CLICKS ]
 USE THIS
TO TAKE THEM BOTH OUT.

41:08.086 --> 41:09.928
I DON'T SEE
A PROBLEM HERE.

41:14.012 --> 41:17.015
[ WAVES CRASHING ]

41:24.943 --> 41:27.696
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

41:36.204 --> 41:39.287
EMILY.

41:39.287 --> 41:41.790
WELL,
THIS IS UNEXPECTED.

41:41.790 --> 41:44.502
[ CLICKS TONGUE ]
YEAH, TO ME, TOO.

41:44.502 --> 41:45.624
THEY DIDN'T STOP YOU
AT THE GATE?

41:45.624 --> 41:46.675
[ CHUCKLES ]

41:46.675 --> 41:48.426
MAN, I REALLY NEED
TO GET A GATE.

41:48.426 --> 41:51.970
IS THIS A BAD TIME?

41:51.970 --> 41:54.302
NO.

41:54.302 --> 41:56.635
GOOD.

41:58.977 --> 42:00.268
SO...

42:00.268 --> 42:01.269
SO...

42:02.190 --> 42:04.402
SO, YOU WANT TO HEAR ABOUT THAT
TIME THAT I WORKED UNDERCOVER?

42:04.402 --> 42:06.815
[ CHUCKLES ]

42:06.815 --> 42:08.647
SHUT UP.
